---
// src/pages/about.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About - I Am That Wisdom Collection" 
  description="Learn about this collection of quotes from Nisargadatta Maharaj's I Am That, created by Eugene Venger as a personal tool for reflection and spiritual growth."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class=" bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
      <article class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
        <header class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">About This Collection</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">A personal journey with timeless wisdom</p>
        </header>

        <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto space-y-8">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gray-800 mb-4">Why I Created This</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              I first encountered "I Am That" about a year ago, and it hit me deep. Now I find myself returning to this book constantly rereading passages.
            </p>

          </section>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-6 py-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-r-lg">
            <p class="text-xl font-serif italic text-gray-800">
              "Love says: 'I am everything'. Wisdom says: 'I am nothing' Between the two my life flows. Since at any point of time and space I can be both the subject and the object of experience, I express it by saying that I am both, and neither, and beyond both.
            </p>
          </blockquote>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gray-800 mb-4">A Personal Note</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              If this collection helps even one person then sharing it has been worthwhile. 
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gray-800 mb-4">Connect</h2>
          
          
